Introduction

Xooos, formerly known as INA, is a South Korean singer, actress, and YouTuber under wavy. She debuted on January 3, 2017, with the digital single "Rainbow".

Before starting her career as a singer, she appeared as an actress in the 2015 drama "The Producers." Meanwhile, after making her official debut, Xooos participated in the survival show "MIXNINE."
